name: Share Location - Google Maps
comment:
This script allows you to share your location using Google maps via Twitter/SMS/E-mail, and utilizes TinyURL to keep map URLs short. If you pin the main tile it will flip over showing your most recent location on the back. I've also integrated an action which you can run to cache your current location. This is checked during each run, allowing you to 'check in' at the same place, even if your GPS is a little off target by allowing for a small variation in accuracy. There is also some URL caching to reduce the need for multiple tinyURLs pointing at the same google maps URL. Actions to clear each of these caches have been included as well.

Oh, and there's an action in there that will prompt you to pick a background color or picture.
